“创造财富”――宝洁大中华区财务总监清华研讨会
演讲题目：Value Creation
演讲人：Suran Suranjan
时间：9月28日（星期三） 晚7：00
地点：就业中心大报告厅
About the Seminar: Value Creation
The Seminar offers a view into how F&amp;A can lead value creation in a business such as P&amp;G’s, from day to day business operations to long term strategic planning. Influencing and leading the business to create value will ensure the company sustains a winning advantage in the competitive consumer products industry.  
About P&amp;G
Founded in 1837, Procter &amp; Gamble is today one of the largest consumer goods manufacturing and marketing companies in the world. We have operations in more than 70 countries, with more than 300 product brands selling in 160 countries.
P&amp;G has a tradition of attracting quality staff. Each year, the company recruits from famous universities aggressive, creative graduates with leadership potential, fine analytical skills, excellent language and communication abilities and a strong cooperative spirit. 
About Mr. Suran Suranjan
Suran obtained his MBA degree from University of Chicago, USA and joined P&amp;G in 1994.
